  <brief_title>Delayed or Direct Ureteroscopy in the Treatment of Pediatric Calcular Anuria</brief_title>
  <official_title>Staged Ureteroscopy After Initial Urinary Drainage Versus Direct Ureteroscopy in the Treatment of Pediatric Obstructive Calcular Anuria</official_title>
  <sponsors>
